(42, 6, 12, 27, 6, 10, 10, NULL, 'Prayer and Devotion', 'Both passages emphasize the act of prayer, highlighting the commitment to communicate with God. Luke describes Jesus praying all night, while Daniel prays three times a day, demonstrating their dedication to spiritual practice.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
