(42, 6, 13, 41, 6, 7, 7, NULL, 'Calling and Sending of the Twelve', 'This connection highlights the continuity of Jesus'' ministry as he first chooses the twelve apostles and then sends them out to preach. Both passages emphasize the significance of the twelve in Jesus'' mission.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
