(42, 6, 14, 41, 1, 19, 19, 'James and John', 'Connection of Discipleship', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of James and John as disciples of Jesus. Luke 6:14 lists them among the apostles, while Mark 1:19 describes their activity as fishermen.', 'parallel', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
